{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be futuristic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Nebula Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0a192f; /* Dark blue background */\n            --secondary-color: #303c52; /* Lighter blue for accents */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --highlight-color: #64ffda; /* Neon cyan for highlights */\n            --font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: var(--font-family);\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50%;\n            left: -50%;\n            width: 200%;\n            height: 200%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.1) 0%, rgba(100, 255, 218, 0) 50%);\n            animation: pulse 5s infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--highlight-color);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--highlight-color), 0 0 20px var(--highlight-color);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--highlight-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .game-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--highlight-color);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.6);\n        }\n\n        .game-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--highlight-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--highlight-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        .scroll-effect {\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(50px);\n            transition: opacity 0.8s ease-out, transform 0.8s ease-out;\n        }\n\n        .scroll-effect.visible {\n            opacity: 1;\n            transform: translateY(0);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Nebula Studios</h1>\n            <p>Crafting worlds beyond imagination.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>At Nebula Studios, we are a collective of passionate developers, artists, and storytellers driven by a singular vision: to create immersive and unforgettable gaming experiences. We blend cutting-edge technology with boundless creativity to forge digital realms that captivate and inspire.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"games\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Games</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-grid\">\n                <div class=\"game-card scroll-effect\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/0a192f/ffffff?text=Game+Art+1\" alt=\"Game Title 1\">\n                    <h3>Cosmic Odyssey</h3>\n                    <p>Embark on an epic interstellar journey across a vast, procedurally generated galaxy. Discover new planets, encounter alien civilizations, and forge your destiny amongst the stars.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card scroll-effect\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/0a192f/ffffff?text=Game+Art+2\" alt=\"Game Title 2\">\n                    <h3>Quantum Shift</h3>\n                    <p>A mind-bending puzzle adventure where you manipulate time and space to solve intricate challenges and unravel the secrets of a collapsing reality.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card scroll-effect\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/0a192f/ffffff?text=Game+Art+3\" alt=\"Game Title 3\">\n                    <h3>Cybernetic Dawn</h3>\n                    <p>Dive into a neon-drenched cyberpunk metropolis. As a rogue agent, fight against mega-corporations and uncover a conspiracy that threatens the city's future.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Connect With Us</h2>\n            <p>Follow our journey and stay updated on our latest projects. Join our community and be a part of the future of gaming.</p>\n            <p>Email: info@nebulastudios.com</p>\n            <p>Social Media: [Link to Twitter] | [Link to Discord] | [Link to Instagram]</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Nebula Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.classList.add('visible');\n                        observer.unobserve(entry.target);\n                    }\n                });\n            }, { threshold: 0.2 });\n\n            const scrollElements = document.querySelectorAll('.scroll-effect');\n            scrollElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}